### 健康檢查
GET http://localhost:8787/

### ----------------------
### KV 基礎 CRUD / TTL / Metadata / List 測試
### ----------------------

### KV set (text)
POST http://localhost:8787/api/kv/set
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "key": "demo:text:hello",
  "value": "world",
  "as": "text",
  "ttl": 60,
  "metadata": {"note": "text with ttl=60"}
}

### KV get (text)
GET http://localhost:8787/api/kv/get/demo:text:hello?type=text

### KV set (json)
POST http://localhost:8787/api/kv/set
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "key": "demo:json:user:1",
  "value": {"id": 1, "name": "George"},
  "as": "json",
  "metadata": {"role": "admin"}
}

### KV get (json)
GET http://localhost:8787/api/kv/get/demo:json:user:1?type=json

### KV list (prefix)
GET http://localhost:8787/api/kv/list?prefix=demo:

### KV list (分頁: 帶 cursor)
# 先取上一個 list 回應的 cursor 值替換 {cursor}
GET http://localhost:8787/api/kv/list?prefix=demo:&cursor={cursor}

### KV delete
DELETE http://localhost:8787/api/kv/demo:text:hello

### 取得所有 todos
GET http://localhost:8787/api/todos

### 建立新 todo
POST http://localhost:8787/api/todos
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "學習 Cloudflare Workers",
  "description": "使用 Hono 框架建立 API",
  "completed": false
}

### 建立另一個 todo
POST http://localhost:8787/api/todos
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "學習 D1 資料庫",
  "description": "整合 SQLite 資料庫",
  "completed": false
}

### 取得單一 todo (替換 {id} 為實際 ID)
GET http://localhost:8787/api/todos/1

### 更新 todo (替換 {id} 為實際 ID)
PUT http://localhost:8787/api/todos/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "學習 Cloudflare Workers (已更新)",
  "description": "使用 Hono 框架建立 API - 已完成",
  "completed": true
}

### 切換 todo 完成狀態 (替換 {id} 為實際 ID)
PATCH http://localhost:8787/api/todos/1/toggle

### 刪除 todo (替換 {id} 為實際 ID)
DELETE http://localhost:8787/api/todos/1
